<h2 id="editors-notes">Editorâ€™s notes</h2>

<p>This lesson will show you how to play the A-major chord with a single finger (through barring the 2nd fret with your index finger). Iâ€™ll show you exactly how to play the chord like this, what the benefits of using this technique are, and when it should &amp; should not be used. Finally, Iâ€™ll play through a handful of song snippets that show this in action.</p>

